@startuml Remote Proxy

interface RemoteService {
    + performOperation(): String
}

class RemoteServiceImpl implements RemoteService {
    + performOperation(): String
}

class RemoteProxy implements RemoteService {
    - serverAddress: String
    - port: int
    + RemoteProxy(address: String, port: int)
    + performOperation(): String
    - sendRequest(data: String): String
}

note top: Handles network communication
note top: Acts as local representative for remote object

RemoteProxy ..> RemoteServiceImpl : network call
Client ..> RemoteProxy : uses

@enduml
